Class Washer

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractComponent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    fr.sorbonne_u.components.ComponentI, fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.interfaces.CyPhyComponentI, WasherImplementationI

    public class Washer
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.AbstractCyPhyComponent
implements WasherImplementationI
    The class Washer implements the washercomponent. The washer can be in 3 differents states : eco, std and performance the washing task are planified the washer automaticly turn on when a task need to start and turn off when he finish to washing
    Author:
    Bello Memmi
